Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.76,0:09:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.53,0:09:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,风见太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.27,0:09:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伯母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.27,0:09:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你们平常那么照顾隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.01,0:09:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿修 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.27,0:09:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给你添了那么多麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.98,0:09:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史密斯已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.11,0:09:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在电视上看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.35,0:09:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈 你怎么认识史密斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.15,0:09:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道老爸他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.29,0:09:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还没跟他们说吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.99,0:09:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.19,0:09:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿修 你是不是知道些什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.21,0:10:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.22,0:10:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为什么一直都不肯跟我连络呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.79,0:10:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算你跟爸爸两个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.12,0:10:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,躲到安全的地方去避难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.53,0:10:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是至少你可以给我个电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.16,0:10:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈不连络你是因为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.33,0:10:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈不想把你卷入危险当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.17,0:10:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.84,0:10:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈 到底是什么事情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.04,0:10:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人 你仔细的听好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.85,0:10:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你爸爸他已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.89,0:10:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈 你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.59,0:10:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你爸爸他已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.48,0:11:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,风见他死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.62,0:11:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么会呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.32,0:11:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正确的说应该是被杀死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.76,0:11:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他被急于获得阿斯拉达的史密斯给杀死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.56,0:11:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.26,0:11:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么重要的事情为什么不告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.43,0:11:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想把隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.60,0:11:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟管生车队的大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.67,0:11:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卷入危险当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.83,0:11:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿修 你再说详细一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.04,0:11:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.48,0:11:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.01,0:11:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五年前我离家出走后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.92,0:11:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以成为F1赛车手为目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.35,0:11:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到欧洲去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.32,0:11:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一段时间一直参加F3车队转战欧洲各地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.06,0:11:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最后终于被F1车队网罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.57,0:12:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个车队 就是史密斯的缺环车队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.41,0:12:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正好就在那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.61,0:12:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,缺环车队已经决定要参加闪电霹雳车赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.42,0:12:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而风见先生就在他们的赛车研发小组里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.88,0:12:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.98,0:12:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是风见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.91,0:12:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,风见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.48,0:12:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是风见叔叔吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.75,0:12:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.65,0:12:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我马上开门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.82,0:13:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你全身都淋湿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.72,0:13:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管怎么样 先进来坐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.06,0:13:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.53,0:13:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你会感冒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.03,0:13:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用管那么多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.43,0:13:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常抱歉这么晚了还来打扰你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.80,0:13:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不是有什么重要的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.43,0:13:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.50,0:13:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你帮我去一赵伦敦好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.74,0:13:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想要请你帮我送个东西\N在今天晚上送到港口去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.88,0:13:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.51,0:13:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是我制造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.41,0:13:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿斯拉达GSX
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.01,0:13:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想把它送回日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.78,0:13:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿斯拉达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.15,0:13:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是阿斯拉达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.62,0:13:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不正是我们车队\N正在研发的闪电霹雳车吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.15,0:13:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么要送回日本去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.52,0:13:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在我没有办法告诉你为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.59,0:13:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是无论如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.83,0:13:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要把阿斯拉达送回日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.46,0:13:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,送到你父亲的手上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.86,0:13:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托你替我办到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.70,0:13:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.40,0:13:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被偷听到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.57,0:13:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿修 今天晚上的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.47,0:13:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就当做没有发生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.44,0:13:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.21,0:13:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道这件事情以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.51,0:13:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怕连你都会有危险的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.95,0:13:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.78,0:13:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,记住 今天晚上什么事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.55,0:14:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都没发生 知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.08,0:14:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.23,0:14:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是管生修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.97,0:14:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史密斯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.20,0:14:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.03,0:14:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更半夜还打电话给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.77,0:14:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想请问一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.97,0:14:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,风见先生有没有去找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.21,0:14:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才来过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.64,0:14:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.91,0:14:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有点急事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.74,0:14:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必须找他谈一谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.11,0:14:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请让他接下电话好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.48,0:14:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是他已经离开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.18,0:14:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么? 他有没有说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.88,0:14:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要到什么地方去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.99,0:14:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是伦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.92,0:14:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就当做今天晚上什么事情都没发生过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.69,0:14:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.76,0:14:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伦敦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.92,0:14:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他有没有说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.79,0:14:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到伦敦什么地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.76,0:14:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他要去机场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.79,0:14:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他说要去西使洛机场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.10,0:14:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这家伙居然真的这么做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.90,0:14:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这到底怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.54,0:14:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,于是隔天我去风见先生家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.81,0:15:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找风见先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.15,0:15:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.12,0:15:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史密斯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.24,0:15:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不要紧吧 振作一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.71,0:15:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.18,0:15:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,风见叔叔 振作一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.25,0:15:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.75,0:15:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿修 是你呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.25,0:15:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我送你去医院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.29,0:15:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 等一下 这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.72,0:15:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个你拿着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.69,0:15:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.56,0:15:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总有一天你会用到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.93,0:15:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿斯拉达就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.73,0:15:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔 我送你到医院去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.20,0:16:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,振作一点 叔叔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.04,0:16:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.75,0:16:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔 叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.09,0:16:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,两天后 风见先生死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.92,0:16:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他就好像被我杀死的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.96,0:16:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.89,0:16:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是哥哥的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.79,0:16:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好的全都是那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.63,0:16:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫史密斯的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.33,0:16:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.06,0:16:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么不通知警察呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.60,0:16:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我当然通知了 可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.33,0:16:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警察根本就不当一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.30,0:16:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,整件事被暗中抹失掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.94,0:16:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那全是史密斯在搞鬼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.71,0:16:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这怎么可能呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.61,0:16:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我绝不原谅史密斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.11,0:16:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然警方他们不敢行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.95,0:16:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就只好靠自己来搜查证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.15,0:16:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我抛弃了管生修这个名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.06,0:16:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用修马赫这个匿名 再度回到赛车界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.96,0:16:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我发誓 总有一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.86,0:16:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要把史密斯的罪行公诸于世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.90,0:17:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是哥哥 你大可以告诉我跟爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.17,0:17:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这件事我不想让隼人知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.80,0:17:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少也要等到史密斯受到制裁以后再说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.61,0:17:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伯母跟我在医院照顾风见先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.94,0:17:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从他口中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.71,0:17:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我听到了一些事情真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.95,0:17:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.97,0:17:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.77,0:17:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.17,0:17:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顺子 阿修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.77,0:17:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 让你们担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.91,0:17:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情为什么会变成这样子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.18,0:17:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我开发的闪电系统阿斯拉达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.35,0:17:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是一切事情的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.25,0:18:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿斯拉达跟以往闪电系统有很大的差异
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.89,0:18:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它有一种功能 可以把人类的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.09,0:18:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当资料来计算处理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.16,0:18:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我原本打算用这个功能\N辅导常处于紧张状态的赛车手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.40,0:18:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当作一个支援的功能而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.41,0:18:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是当阿斯拉达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.37,0:18:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真正的完成了以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.74,0:18:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这能力却远远超过我的想像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.71,0:18:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿斯拉达把使用者的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.22,0:18:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,换成资料来储存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.08,0:18:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自我成长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.92,0:18:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最后甚至可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.92,0:18:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算出比赛对手的心理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.43,0:18:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这或许可以说是高智能方程式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.76,0:18:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当中最理想的电脑系统了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.13,0:18:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是却有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.07,0:18:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想要把阿斯拉达的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.73,0:18:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用在其他的用途上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.11,0:18:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个人他就是史密斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.27,0:18:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他要用在什么用途上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.08,0:18:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史密斯他想把阿斯拉达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.14,0:18:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用来当武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.38,0:19:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果阿斯拉达的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.08,0:19:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被用来专门杀人的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.54,0:19:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我绝对不能让阿斯拉达变成杀人的工具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.88,0:19:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.51,0:19:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.49,0:19:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要跟我开发出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.09,0:19:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿斯拉达GSX
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.09,0:19:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起逃出史密斯的掌握
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.86,0:19:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿斯拉达是为了在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.06,0:19:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赛车场的战场中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.26,0:19:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让人活下来而开发出来的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.50,0:19:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿斯拉达的原设计图
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.27,0:19:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经被我烧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.20,0:19:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史密斯知道了这一点可能会把矛头放在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.14,0:19:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚刚完成的阿斯拉达身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.98,0:20:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你才会叫我把完成的\N阿斯拉达送到日本去是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.91,0:20:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经把完成的阿斯拉达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.35,0:20:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一定会在日本完成我的梦想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.26,0:20:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顺子 你也要快点躲起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.56,0:20:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一次史密斯的目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.56,0:20:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能就是知道真相的你跟阿修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.20,0:20:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.50,0:20:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿修 那个东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.44,0:20:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.10,0:20:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个东西交给你保管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.57,0:20:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果史密斯来抢\N你又没有办法保护它的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.51,0:20:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就把它毁掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.31,0:20:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那这个是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.12,0:20:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是另一个阿斯拉达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.89,0:20:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公 你振作一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.39,0:20:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.42,0:20:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.63,0:20:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.16,0:20:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸对你一直没有做到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.96,0:20:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一个父亲应该做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.15,0:21:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸一直很想哪一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.65,0:21:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给你做一辆属于你的车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.39,0:21:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.06,0:21:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人 妈妈之所以会把这件事情告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.00,0:21:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是想要你了解 爸爸他是抱着怎样的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.07,0:21:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是在怎样的心情下来制造阿斯拉达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.21,0:21:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚至不惜赌上性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.94,0:21:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来保护阿斯拉达的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.88,0:21:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,骗人 爸爸怎么会死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.89,0:21:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.79,0:22:16.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他人目光没有在背后注视着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.45,0:22:23.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面向前方 生存下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.56,0:22:27.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为肩负着使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.78,0:22:30.28,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相互信任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.30,0:22:37.03,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放下双手 仰望天空时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.76,0:22:40.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相互信任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.18,0:22:48.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的笑容是我心中的支柱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.61,0:22:55.87,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有现在加倍努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.87,0:23:00.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才能有明天的辉煌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.36,0:23:05.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此 不用后悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.87,0:23:11.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向着自己树立的目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.80,0:23:16.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迎着风前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.24,0:23:21.36,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最终我们会是胜利者

